    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "While looking straight down the barrel of this *+1 striking blunderbuss*, the spark gun's magical core is visible amid several reflectors. All damage dealt by a *thundercrasher* is sonic damage. On a critical hit, the target must succeed at a Fortitude save against your class DC or be deafened for 1 minute.",
